Package: SBF
Title: R package to compute Shared Basis Factorization (SBF) 
Version: 1.0.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Amal",
           family = "Thomas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "amalthom@usc.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4494-4487"))
Description: The R package implements Shared Basis Factorization (SBF) and
    Approximate Shared Basis Factorization (A-SBF). Shared Basis Factorization
    (SBF) is an exact joint diagonalization approach. Approximate Shared Basis
    Factorization is an extension of the SBF approach.
